# Todo Web Application â€“ Backend

A full-stack web application backend that allows users to register, login, and  manage their personal tasks.

## Features

- User registration and login with secure password hashing 
- CRUD operations for notes
- REST API for frontend integration
- Session management using HttpSession

## Technologies

- Java 
- Spring Boot
- MySQL
- REST API

## Frontend

The frontend repository is available here: https://github.com/ivanyoslaszlo/Todo-Frontend.git

## Deployment

The live application is available at: https://ivanyoslaszlo.hu
